      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "🔒 Privacy boundaries: mitmproxy extracts only the URL path (content ID) — never message bodies, video content, or passwords.\nGroq / Anthropic receive only: {title, category, platform, age_profile}. No personal data leaves Canada (OCI ca-toronto-1) except to Groq/Anthropic APIs for AI scoring.",
